        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> and <strong>cauliflower florets</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> over a high heat and bring to the boil</p><p>Cook for 10-15 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once done, drain, return them to the pot and cover to keep warm</p>",
      "order": 4,
