    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper and set aside until later</p><p>Add the <strong>flaked almonds </strong>to a<strong> food processor </strong>with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and the <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>,<strong> half </strong>the<strong> dried thyme </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>romesco mix</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
